name: zZZ
description:
"I was working at home in front of the computer while my cat fell asleep on my bed.
Everything seemed so peaceful. I wish I could share the moment with you.
Today is a lovely day in November 2021."

Normally he is a smart and naughty cat. He likes to play around and interrupts my work in many ways. As you can guess, I still love him with all my heart.

Spread the love and warmth to all of you. Have a nice day!
